# forge-cms.dev — REST Client requests
# VS Code extension: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
#
# Usage:
#   1. Run the app: go run . (SECRET=... must be set)
#   2. Copy the token logged to stdout into @token below, OR set ADMIN_TOKEN.
#   3. Click "Send Request" above any ### block.
#
# The app logs an admin token on startup when ADMIN_TOKEN env var is not set.
# Token has no expiry (TTL=0). Rotate by changing SECRET and restarting.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── 1. Health check ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/_health
Accept: application/json

### ─── 2. Create a Post (draft) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Response includes "ID" and "Slug" — copy Slug into @postSlug below.

# @name createPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/devlog
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Title": "Hello from Forge",
  "Body": "This is the first devlog post, created via the content API.",
  "Tags": ["forge", "go", "cms"]
}

### ─── 3. Publish the Post ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Replace SLUG with the Slug value returned in step 2.
# PUT /{prefix}/{slug} is the update endpoint; setting Status = "published"
# triggers the publish lifecycle event (sitemap regeneration, feed update).

@postSlug = REPLACE_WITH_SLUG_FROM_STEP_2

PUT {{baseUrl}}/devlog/{{postSlug}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Title": "Hello from Forge",
  "Body": "This is the first devlog post, created via the content API.",
  "Tags": ["forge", "go", "cms"],
  "Status": "published"
}

### ─── 4. Create a DocPage (draft) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Response includes "ID" and "Slug" — copy Slug into @docSlug below.

# @name createDoc
POST {{baseUrl}}/docs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Title": "Getting Started",
  "Body": "Welcome to Forge. This guide covers installation and your first app.",
  "Section": "introduction",
  "Order": 1
}

### ─── 5. Verify published Post is publicly visible ─────────────────────────
# No auth required — Forge only serves Published items on public GET endpoints.

GET {{baseUrl}}/devlog/{{postSlug}}
Accept: application/json
